text: Frederik Finisie (c. 1958 â€“ 5 December 2024) was a Surinamese politician. As a member of the National Democratic Party (NDP) he served for 22 years as a member of the National Assembly from 1996 to 2018. From August 2018 to 2020 he was District Commissioner of Brokopondo. In 2021 he moved from NDP to General Liberation and Development Party.
